    <pre>My guess here (mcandre, let me know if I'm wrong), is that after checking some updates boxes, 
mcandre clicked the Save link for a particular project, rather than the "Save all projects" button at the 
bottom. Clicking Save does a full page update, blowing away the other checkbox changes.

See <a href="http://openhatch.org/bugs/issue515">http://openhatch.org/bugs/issue515</a> for another expression of this problem.</pre>
   </td>
