the right value.

At this point, what we need to do is make sure the 
receive_maintainer_updates_{{project.id}} form name is processed properly 
by the Python backend.

That would be a good thing to write an automated test for. (I don't know 
if you're interested in contributing some Python code, but if so, then we 
should keep talking about how that would work.)

Either way, thanks for all the good research you've done so far!</pre>
